<P>Oh, and to note, before someone says "omg you guys are so unoriginal, FFXI already did this." I'd agree, it's not an original idea. I played FFXI a bit when it came out and their "Artifact Armor" which is similar to epics was really impressive.&nbsp;Below is a good page to view what they have for epic armor for each job (class) in their game for each race. Note for example that the Red Mage armor (Red armor with a feather in the cap) for a Taru Taru (the short dudes) looks very similar to the Red Mage armor of the Elvan Male (the tall elvish dudes...duh).</P>
<P><A href="http://www.randomdialogue.net/gallery/ffxiarmor" target=_blank>ttp://www.randomdialogue.net/gallery/ffxiarmor</A></P>
<P>While the art is a little too Asian for EverQuest, it does give a good example of how epic armor would work and feel.</P>
				
